lyrics:
[Verse]
Late at night, a secret call
To a team of agents, standing tall
Masters of magic, tough and brave
Dealing with creatures the world can't save

[Chorus]
We're A.R.C.A.N.E., the warriors unseen
Fighting for justice in the shadows we dream
With powers arcane, we'll stand side by side
A team of special agents on this mystical ride
style: County Love Song with a Male singer
